headline: New Ownership of Pak Mail in Hazel Park, Michigan Offers Shipping and Office Services--with More Ways to Help More People in their Community
summary: Annex Brands, Inc., a leading franchisor in the packing, shipping, and office services industries, is pleased to announce the successful transfer of ownership of an existing Pak Mail location in Hazel Park, MI to new owner, Hemang Trivedi. This Pak Mail location has served the community for the last 26 years and this transition to new ownership ensures that the community will benefit from essential shipping and office services.
